OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start in parts of the
OL,6,Fwest, breaking up during the morning.
OL,7,FThen a dry day everywhere with some
OL,8,Fgood spells of sunshine, and becoming
OL,9,Fvery warm to hot.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA warm sunny evening then dry
OL,12,Fwith clear periods overnight. Some low
OL,13,Fcloud developing over Dumfries and
OL,14,FGalloway. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FAny cloud in the southwest
OL,17,Fburning off in the morning. Then dry
OL,18,Fwith some good sunny spells and
OL,19,Fbecoming very warm to hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
