OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry on
OL,6,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,7,Fbecoming very warm or hot. Cloudier in
OL,8,Fthe east on Saturday with some haar,
OL,9,Fbrighter and warmer west. Sunday dry
OL,10,Fwith some sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
